data.title: ALLHC Definitive Information Statement 2020 v5 - 3 19 20 1 PDF
data.meta_description: ALLHC-Definitive-Information-Statement-2020-v5_3-19-20-1.pdf - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document provides notice of the annual stockholders' meeting of Ayalaland Logistics Holdings Corp. to be held virtually on April 13, 2020 at 10:00 AM. The agenda includes ratification of past board decisions, election of directors and auditors, and approval of financial statements. Stockholders must register by March 31 to attend or vote remotely. A proxy form is attached for stockholders to authorize the chairman to vote on their behalf.
